722392f-a.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 109th Street
722392f-a.text:
1504 and 1506 Park Avenue, west side, between 109th and 110th Streets,
showing a tiny one-story frame shoe store tucked in between the
two buildings.
July 6, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

715013f-b.title: Manhattan: 109th Street (East) - Park Avenue
715013f-b.text:
(1)
61-65 East 109th Street, north side, between Park and Madison
Aves. Building shown is a synagogue (Nachlath 2'vi).
July 6, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from a different angle.
April 26, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
